          text: "Do you ever find yourself falling into the “discount trap?”",
          time: "2018-02-10T08:45:28.291Z",
          id: "323sa680b3249760ea21rt47",
          name: "Frank Powell",
          avatar: "/assets/images/faces/13.jpg",
          status: "online",
          mood: ""
        },
        {
